import React from 'react'
import ReactDom from 'react-dom'
import App from './App'

import './index.css'

ReactDom.render(
  <App />,
  document.getElementById('menu')
)

ReactDom.render(
  <Navbar />,
  document.getElementById('nav')
)

ReactDom.render(
  <Jumbotron />,
  document.getElementById('content')
)
